quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,77,"Mbela …ďe nganndataa wonde Alla Mbo anndi ko …ďe cuu…óta e ko …ďe …ďaŇčnginta."
  2,78,"Na woodi he ma…ď…ďe humambinnee…ďe …ďe nganndaa he deftere ndee sonaa janngugol penaale …óe …ďe nganndinaa, …ďe ngonaani so wonaa sikkude tan."
  2,79,"Bone woodanii …ďeen winndiroo…ďe deftere nde juu…óe ma…ď…ďe e…ďe mbi'a …óum ko to Alla iwri haa …ďe coodira nde coodgu hoyngu, yoo bone wonan …ďe he ko juu…óe ma…ď…ďe mbinndi e kala ko …ďe paggitii heen."
  2,80,"∆Āe mbi'i jayngol memataa min sinaa bal…óe see…óa wi' …ďe mbela on ke…ďii fodoore Alla te Alla luutndotaako aadi Makko wolla ngon-…óon ko haalde he Alla ko on nganndanaa."
  2,81,"Ko goonga kala mbo faggitii bonannde bon…ói makko piilii mo, ko …ďeen ngoni yim…ďe jayngol luttoo…ďe toon."
  2,82,"∆Āeen goong…óin…ďe …ďe ngolli mo∆ī∆īereeji ko …ďeen ngoni yim…ďe aljanna luttoo…ďe toon."
  2,83,"Min …ďamii fodoore he …ďi…ď…ďe Isra'iil taa ndewee sonaa Alla , mo∆ī∆īon he jibnaa…ďe e jiidaa…ďe e waay…óu…ďe e waas…ďe o…óon kaalana yim…ďe …ďee ko mo∆ī∆īi ndarnon juulde tottiron asakal …ďaawo …óuum cali-…óon …óuurni-…óon so wonaa see…óa he moo…óon."